'''克里斯多福·弗萊森'''（{{lang-en|Christopher Flexen}}，{{bd|1994年|7月1日|}}），亦昵称为'''克里斯·弗萊森'''（{{Lang-en|Chris Flexen}}），為[[美國職業棒球大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]的投手，目前效力於[[西雅圖水手|西雅圖水手]]。他先前曾效力過大聯盟的[[紐約大都會|紐約大都會]]與[[KBO聯賽|韓國職棒]]的[[斗山熊|斗山熊]]。

==職業生涯==
===紐約大都會===
弗萊森於2012年開始在[[美國職棒小聯盟|小聯盟]]打球，2017年7月27日登上大聯盟。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.nj.com/mets/index.ssf/2017/07/mets_prospect_chris_flexen_set_to_make_big_league.html|title=Mets' Chris Flexen set to make MLB debut: What to know|work=NJ.com|access-date=July 28, 2017|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190207072733/https://www.nj.com/mets/index.ssf/2017/07/mets_prospect_chris_flexen_set_to_make_big_league.html}}</ref>他生涯首次先發被擊出5支安打失4分。而且他在初登板面對的第一位打者Manuel Margot，第三球就被敲出全壘打。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Mastracco|first1=Abbey|title=Mets' Chris Flexen shelled in MLB debut {{!}} Rapid Reaction|url=http://www.nj.com/mets/index.ssf/2017/07/mets_chris_flexen_shelled_in_mlb_debut_rapid_react.html|accessdate=September 13, 2017|work=[[NJ.com|NJ.com]]|date=July 28, 2017|archive-date=2019-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190207072754/https://www.nj.com/mets/index.ssf/2017/07/mets_chris_flexen_shelled_in_mlb_debut_rapid_react.html}}</ref>8月8日，他先發5.1局失3分拿下大聯盟首勝。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kerber|first1=Fred|title=Chris Flexen picks up first MLB win thanks to Mets’ power display|url=https://nypost.com/2017/08/08/chris-flexen-picks-up-first-mlb-win-thanks-to-mets-power-display/|accessdate=August 9, 2017|work=[[New_York_Post|New York Post]]|date=August 9, 2017|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112020704/http://nypost.com/2017/08/08/chris-flexen-picks-up-first-mlb-win-thanks-to-mets-power-display/}}</ref>

2018年，他被評價為大都會隊上第9號新秀。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/mets-2018-top-30-prospects-list-led-by-gimenez/c-266724882?tid=151437456|title=Gimenez leads new Mets Top 30 Prospects list|publisher=MLB.com|accessdate=February 22, 2018|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612141054/https://www.mlb.com/news/mets-2018-top-30-prospects-list-led-by-gimenez/c-266724882?tid=151437456}}</ref>並在5月19日重返大聯盟。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Botte|first1=Peter|title=Mets made these roster moves ahead of Diamondbacks game|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/mets/mets-roster-moves-diamondbacks-game-article-1.3998769|accessdate=May 19, 2018|work=[[New_York_Daily_News|New York Daily News]]|date=May 19, 2018|archive-date=2018-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180810211445/http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/mets/mets-roster-moves-diamondbacks-game-article-1.3998769}}</ref>不過這年他僅出賽4場比賽，防禦率高達12.76。而且他在8月初還因為膝蓋動手術造成球季提前結束。

===斗山熊===
2019年12月6日，弗萊森遭到球隊放進指定讓渡名單內。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sny.tv/mets/news/mets-sign-free-agent-reliever-brad-brach/312100014|title=Mets sign free agent reliever Brad Brach|author=Danny Abriano|website=[[SportsNet_New_York|SNY]]|date=December 6, 2019|accessdate=December 7, 2019|archive-date=2020-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200221064517/https://www.sny.tv/mets/news/mets-sign-free-agent-reliever-brad-brach/312100014}}</ref>隔天他便與韓職的斗山熊簽下1年合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20191208002100315|title=Ex-MLB pitcher Chris Flexen signs with KBO's Doosan Bears|work=Yonhap News|date=December 8, 2019|access-date=2020-12-20|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919070459/https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20191208002100315}}</ref>而到了韓職投球的弗萊森表現復活，整年拿下8勝4敗，防禦率為3.01，K/9值更是高達10.2。

===西雅圖水手===
2020年12月9日，弗萊森與水手隊簽下2年475萬美元的合約。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2020/12/mariners-sign-chris-flexen-kbo.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-12-20 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208173414/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2020/12/mariners-sign-chris-flexen-kbo.html }}</ref>

